===== ListView =====

A virtual list widget. It is deprecated in 0.7.x and not planned to be ported 
to qooxdoo 0.8. Please use the Table widget instead, which is part of the 
framework for a very long time now.

If you don't want to migrate to Table and/or rely on functionality that only 
ListView provides, you may have to port it to 0.8 yourself. This project can be 
used as a place of collaboration for such a port.
